2113
01:54:53.200 --> 01:54:56.100
Nay, if I turn mine eyesupon myself,

2114
01:54:56.100 --> 01:54:57.830
I find myself a traitorwith the rest,

2115
01:54:57.830 --> 01:55:00.600
