01:55:30.500 --> 01:55:31.630
Alack the heavy day

2126
01:55:31.630 --> 01:55:33.830
that I have worn so manywinters out

2127
01:55:33.830 --> 01:55:37.570
and know not now what nameto call myself.

2128
01:55:38.770 --> 01:55:45.270
Oh, that I were a mockeryking of snow,

2129
01:55:45.270 --> 01:55:50.430
standing before the sun ofBolingbroke,

2130
