2166
01:58:44.200 --> 01:58:46.670
The shadow of my sorrow.

2167
01:58:47.170 --> 01:58:48.230
Ha!

2168
01:58:52.530 --> 01:58:53.530
Let's see.

2169
01:58:53.530 --> 01:58:56.000
'Tis very true.

2170
01:58:56.000 --> 01:58:59.500
My grief lies all within.

2171
01:58:59.500 --> 01:59:02.730
