2180
01:59:40.200 --> 01:59:42.300
Name it, fair cousin.

2181
01:59:42.300 --> 01:59:44.100
Fair cousin?

2182
01:59:45.430 --> 01:59:47.800
I am greater than a king,

2183
01:59:47.800 --> 01:59:50.670
for when I was a king,

2184
01:59:50.670 --> 01:59:53.430
