2188
02:00:05.900 --> 02:00:07.500
And shall I have?

2189
02:00:07.500 --> 02:00:08.870
You shall.

2190
02:00:08.870 --> 02:00:10.830
Then give me leave to go.

2191
02:00:12.230 --> 02:00:13.230
Whither?

2192
02:00:13.230 --> 02:00:21.370
